g src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"食食食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"本來今日想去龍門<br />\n但不如幫下小店啦<br />\n聽日打算繼續食<br />\n但見有人開POST<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣黃店無人食嘅屌<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2160678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2160678</a><br />\n<br />\n依家好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"幫小店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c2f57fdcd41b1343f575cedafe580d5f424fcd","tid":2160534,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"啲皮望落去好薄<br />\n勁想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eafdf6325c876cd7b0e98968e648ab5d62063a","tid":2160534,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"灣仔銅鑼灣返工食野好正<br />\n好多餐廳質素都唔錯，係普遍貴少少<br />\n俾我真係食到窮<br />\n好彩我mk做野"},{"pid":"ce0e10027872d9d414c33088a11e2a695e68d123","tid":2160534,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e72d974eef715940710fcd2f1f2afda0cd9476b","tid":2160534,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea8055c8e16e98892fd55fe11e69e87054a0b23","tid":2160534,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599c8610ad87bed3ef254ff65dd5cde2fb150bf8","tid":2160534,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:48:37.000Z","msg":"34蚊真係好撚抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多外賣 你唔問佢都唔會俾額外調料俾你<br />\n成日都側側膊 仲要外賣個類少過堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望毒男巴介紹多d<br />\n等我下次返香港 可以跟你d po去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"原價42<br />\n餃餃陣好似熊貓先有<br />\n堂食唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過堂食味道一定最好<br />\n唔夠配料又可以加<br />\n你呢個有錢人外國大把好野食啦<br />\n唔洗返黎食平野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"我係香港最鐘意食小店<br />\n小店唔係連鎖 有水準少少<br />\n你俾我揀我好樂意同你交換<br />\n你平時d野啱我口味多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"唔好盲目撐小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少部份係好用心，高質<br />\n但係有好多都係hea做，啲野唔入得口<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔鍾意食連鎖<br />\n但不得不承認連鎖普遍都差極有個譜<br />\n味道應該好過一半或以上既小店<br />\n黃色小店應該都要學下人地經營方式"},{"pid":"3ac01a9ffc512d4e04e07a647ecbc05e223f5dac","tid":2160534,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"52ad7373e517cd93bbc84fc7ab15683b43657409","tid":2160534,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-1